  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hexagroove combines strategy, rhythm, and action in a blend of self-expression. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal as a DJ is to trigger musical loops while following 6 rules of music making to polish your artistic skills. Action swings from contemplative to frantic as you move between song sections in one of 15 dance genres. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over time you'll unlock new music, DJ tricks, and club venues to play in with up to 3 friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/9c908e9bdbec6994a70af1b1e351a3cd.webp?t=1769351753\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose and combine musical pieces across 720 loops from 15 dance genres</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Follow UI lighting cues to clear the level in one of 8 club venues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Time rhythmic elements and audio filters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Perform DJ tricks to maximise your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-4P local multiplayer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/c8c019ab4c745afad7539bd9c5041654.webp?t=1769351753\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hexagroove follows a tour of classic dance genres to modern trends, each split into 48 combinable looping blocks allowing you to create music to your own tastes.  Sound design by: Legowelt, Yuji Takenouchi, Runners Club 95, Cylon, no. 9, Big Skapinsky, TWIDDL, Kristoffer Wallman, lallow, Mr. YT / missing soul, Junya Nakano, and Yasuo Sato</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALSO CHECK OUT THE DEMO FOR OUR SECOND GAME, <strong>BACKBEAT</strong>!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/a53d28b21d97fc1bc71a36a13f45fb10.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hexagroove combines strategy, rhythm, and action in a blend of self-expression. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal as a DJ is to trigger musical loops while following 6 rules of music making to polish your artistic skills. Action swings from contemplative to frantic as you move between song sections in one of 15 dance genres. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over time you'll unlock new music, DJ tricks, and club venues to play in with up to 3 friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/9c908e9bdbec6994a70af1b1e351a3cd.webp?t=1769351753\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/432807fa6b82a017d36ff94b64aae5dc.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose and combine musical pieces across 720 loops from 15 dance genres</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Follow UI lighting cues to clear the level in one of 8 club venues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Time rhythmic elements and audio filters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Perform DJ tricks to maximise your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1-4P local multiplayer</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/c8c019ab4c745afad7539bd9c5041654.webp?t=1769351753\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.poster.avif?t=1769351753\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.webm?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396140/extras/248bbe3a246eb1d026009e4259ca5d92.mp4?t=1769351753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hexagroove follows a tour of classic dance genres to modern trends, each split into 48 combinable looping blocks allowing you to create music to your own tastes.  Sound design by: Legowelt, Yuji Takenouchi, Runners Club 95, Cylon, no. 9, Big Skapinsky, TWIDDL, Kristoffer Wallman, lallow, Mr. YT / missing soul, Junya Nakano, and Yasuo Sato</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ALSO CHECK OUT THE DEMO FOR OUR SECOND GAME, <strong>BACKBEAT</strong>!</p>",
